trans-unit.source: Represents the abstract base class from which several classes in the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description"></xref> namespace are derived.
trans-unit.target: 몇 가지 클래스는 추상 기본 클래스를 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description"> </xref> 네임 스페이스에서 파생 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Several classes are derived from this class: - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Message> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.PortType> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Service> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Types> This base class contains only one property, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem.Documentation%2A> property, which represents the text documentation for a specific WSDL (Web Services Description Language) element.
trans-unit.target: 여러 클래스가이 클래스 로부터 파생 됩니다:- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Message>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.PortType>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Service>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Types>하나의 속성을 포함 하는이 기본 클래스는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem.Documentation%2A>속성으로, 특정 WSDL (Web Services Description Language) 요소에 대 한 텍스트 문서를 나타냅니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem.Documentation%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Types> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Service> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.PortType> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Message> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"></xref> class.
Gets or sets the text documentation for the instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 인스턴스에 대 한 텍스트 설명서를 가져오거나 설정 합니다.는 <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: In a derived class, this property represents the text comments added to an element of the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: 파생된 클래스에서이 속성은 XML 웹 서비스의 요소에 추가 된 텍스트 설명을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation is an empty string ("").
A string that represents the documentation for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 설명서를 나타내는 문자열의 <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the documentation element for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Documentation 요소에 대 한를 가져오거나 설정 합니다.는 <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: This property contains XML elements that are added to a description of an XML Web service to document it.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성에 문서화 하는 XML 웹 서비스에 대 한 설명을 추가 하는 XML 요소를 포함 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"></xref> that represents the documentation for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"> </xref> 나타내는 대 한 설명서는 <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.DocumentableItem"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an array of type <xref href="System.Xml.XmlAttribute"></xref> that represents attribute extensions of WSDL to comply with Web Services Interoperability (WS-I) Basic Profile 1.1.
trans-unit.target: 형식의 배열을 가져오거나 설정 합니다. <xref href="System.Xml.XmlAttribute"> </xref> 나타내는 웹 서비스 상호 운용성을 준수 하는 WSDL의 확장 특성 있는지 (WS-I) Basic Profile 1.1.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the dictionary of namespace prefixes and namespaces used to preserve namespace prefixes and namespaces when a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> object is constructed.
trans-unit.target: 네임 스페이스 접두사 및 네임 스페이스 접두사와 네임 스페이스를 유지 하는 데 사용 되는 네임 스페이스의 사전을 가져오거나 설정 합니다. 때는 <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> 개체가 만들어집니다.
